data.description: Proudly presented by Suzanne Nelson of Properties Unlimited. For more information call/text 605.347.1488. This is the home you have been waiting for! This 4-bedroom, 2-bath home is ready for you to move in. No honey-do list! Inside and out this home has been updated and is bright and fresh. Completely updated kitchen with new appliances, lights, and countertops. The dining room is bright with the light from a new Anderson sliding glass door that opens to the fenced back yard. The living room opens to more than 600 square feet of deck overlooking Sturgis. Prepare to be the "must watch spot" for 4th of July fireworks for all the years you call 122 David Drive home! 3-bedrooms on the main level, an additional bedroom with egress window in the basement. Main level bedrooms have ceiling fans! New flooring throughout both levels. A spacious laundry room with folding counter and sink. Additional storage room with workbench. Another workbench in the garage. Electricity to the storage shed. If you are looking for a home that is walkable to Sturgis Elementary, you won't get closer than this!
